data.description: Ready to go!  New foundation w warranty and buyers pick the carpet prior to close!  This charming starter home is a delightful blend of practicality and comfort. Located in the highly-sought after Birdville ISD, the home is in walking distance to O.H. Stowe Elementary. Inside this open layout home, you'll be greeted by inviting rooms, beautiful bathrooms and bedrooms with large closets. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts a large pantry, stainless steel appliances, and generous counter space and storage. The home also features an oversized two car garage, a sunlit utility room that doubles as a flex space and a large barn-style shed for even more possibilities .This home has endless potential. But that's not all—you have the unique opportunity to put your personal stamp on this home by selecting the carpet of your choice (samples onsite). Imagine walking into a space that not only meets your practical needs but also reflects your style and taste. Fridge and W and D convey!
